#include <iostream>
#include<stdio.h>
#include <algorithm>
using namespace std;

int main() {
	int n;
	int doll_size[10000];
	int t;
	scanf("%d",&t);
	while(t--){
	scanf("%d",&n);
	doll_size[n];
	for(int i=0;i<n;i++){
		scanf("%d",&doll_size[i]);
	}
	sort (doll_size, doll_size+n);
	int count=0;
	for(int i=n-1;i>0;i--){
	   if(doll_size[i]>doll_size[i-1]){
	     count++;
	    // printf("%d ",count);
	   }
	  
	}
	if(n==count+1)
	  printf("YES\n");
	 else
	 printf("NO\n");
	 
	}
	return 0; 
}
